### CCR-NEW (pending §10 of Players_HandHistory_API.md) — WSOP LIVE Chip Count Sync Webhook
###
### Cycle 20 Wave 4 (issue #447) — S9 QA contract test
### SSOT:
###   docs/2. Development/2.2 Backend/APIs/WSOP_LIVE_Chip_Count_Sync.md  (v1.0.0, contract)
###   docs/2. Development/2.2 Backend/APIs/WebSocket_Events.md §4.2.11   (chip_count_synced)
###   docs/2. Development/2.5 Shared/Chip_Count_State.md                 (state machine)
###
### 검증 범위:
### - A 정상 (202 Accepted + ws_event_dispatched=true)
### - B HMAC 위반 (401 SIGNATURE_INVALID)
### - C timestamp drift > 300s (401 TIMESTAMP_DRIFT, replay 차단)
### - D Idempotent (snapshot_id 재전송 → 200 already_processed, broadcast 재발행 안 함)
### - E Idempotency-Key ↔ body.snapshot_id 불일치 (409 IDEMPOTENCY_MISMATCH)
### - F 알 수 없는 table_id (422 TABLE_UNKNOWN)
###
### HMAC 계산 (X-WSOP-Signature) — WSOP_LIVE_Chip_Count_Sync.md §6.1
###   canonical_string = "POST\n/api/wsop-live/chip-count-snapshot\n" + timestamp + "\n" + sha256(body).hex()
###   signature        = hmac_sha256(WSOP_LIVE_WEBHOOK_SECRET, canonical_string).hex()
###
### 본 시나리오는 httpyac/REST Client 양쪽 호환. HMAC 값은 환경 변수로 주입한다.
### .env 정의 (or 실행 환경 export):
###   WSOP_LIVE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=<32 bytes hex>
###   WSOP_HMAC_VALID=<위 절차로 계산된 hex digest, body 내용에 맞춰 사전 계산>
###   WSOP_HMAC_INVALID=deadbeef0000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000beef
###   WSOP_TS_NOW=<ISO8601 UTC, 현재 시각 ±300s 이내>
###   WSOP_TS_OLD=<ISO8601 UTC, 현재로부터 1시간 이상 과거 — replay 시뮬레이션>

@host = http://localhost:18001
@endpoint = /api/wsop-live/chip-count-snapshot

@snap_ok            = 8a7e9c4e-5d3b-4f1a-9c2e-7b6a0e8f1d3c
@snap_dup           = 8a7e9c4e-5d3b-4f1a-9c2e-7b6a0e8f1d3c
@snap_mismatch      = c1d2e3f4-0000-4000-8000-000000000099
@snap_unknown_table = 5b3d2c1a-9e8f-4a7b-8c6d-1f2e3d4c5b6a

@hmac_valid   = {{$dotenv WSOP_HMAC_VALID}}
@hmac_invalid = {{$dotenv WSOP_HMAC_INVALID}}
@ts_now       = {{$dotenv WSOP_TS_NOW}}
@ts_old       = {{$dotenv WSOP_TS_OLD}}

### A. 정상 webhook → 202 Accepted
### 기대: status="accepted", snapshot_id echo, ws_event_dispatched=true
### Side-effect: chip_count_snapshots 9 rows INSERT, lobby/cc:17/overlay:17 broadcast
POST {{host}}{{endpoint}}
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
X-WSOP-Signature: {{hmac_valid}}
X-WSOP-Timestamp: {{ts_now}}
Idempotency-Key: {{snap_ok}}
User-Agent: WSOPLive-ChipCountSync/1.0.0

{
  "snapshot_id": "{{snap_ok}}",
  "break_id": 1024,
  "table_id": 17,
  "recorded_at": "{{ts_now}}",
  "seats": [
    {"seat_number": 1, "player_id": 901, "chip_count": 125000},
    {"seat_number": 2, "player_id": 902, "chip_count": 87500},
    {"seat_number": 3, "player_id": null, "chip_count": 0},
    {"seat_number": 4, "player_id": 904, "chip_count": 211000},
    {"seat_number": 5, "player_id": 905, "chip_count": 64000},
    {"seat_number": 6, "player_id": 906, "chip_count": 150500},
    {"seat_number": 7, "player_id": 907, "chip_count": 92000},
    {"seat_number": 8, "player_id": 908, "chip_count": 175500},
    {"seat_number": 9, "player_id": 909, "chip_count": 0}
  ]
}

###

### B. HMAC 검증 실패 → 401 SIGNATURE_INVALID
### 기대: {"error": "SIGNATURE_INVALID"}, DB INSERT 안 됨, broadcast 안 됨
POST {{host}}{{endpoint}}
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
X-WSOP-Signature: {{hmac_invalid}}
X-WSOP-Timestamp: {{ts_now}}
Idempotency-Key: 11111111-2222-4333-8444-555555555555
User-Agent: WSOPLive-ChipCountSync/1.0.0

{
  "snapshot_id": "11111111-2222-4333-8444-555555555555",
  "break_id": 1024,
  "table_id": 17,
  "recorded_at": "{{ts_now}}",
  "seats": [
    {"seat_number": 1, "player_id": 901, "chip_count": 125000}
  ]
}

###

### C. Replay attack (timestamp drift > 300s) → 401 TIMESTAMP_DRIFT
### 기대: {"error": "TIMESTAMP_DRIFT", "received": "...", "now": "..."}
### 시나리오: 1시간 이상 과거 timestamp + 정상 HMAC (replay 시도)
POST {{host}}{{endpoint}}
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
X-WSOP-Signature: {{hmac_valid}}
X-WSOP-Timestamp: {{ts_old}}
Idempotency-Key: 22222222-3333-4444-8555-666666666666
User-Agent: WSOPLive-ChipCountSync/1.0.0

{
  "snapshot_id": "22222222-3333-4444-8555-666666666666",
  "break_id": 1024,
  "table_id": 17,
  "recorded_at": "{{ts_old}}",
  "seats": [
    {"seat_number": 1, "player_id": 901, "chip_count": 125000}
  ]
}

###

### D. Idempotent — 동일 snapshot_id 재전송 → 200 already_processed
### 기대: status="already_processed", ws_event_dispatched=false (broadcast 재발행 안 함)
### 사전 조건: A 가 먼저 실행되어 snap_ok 가 commit 되어 있어야 함.
### immutable append 정책 (§7.3): body 내용 달라도 첫 commit 데이터만 truth.
POST {{host}}{{endpoint}}
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
X-WSOP-Signature: {{hmac_valid}}
X-WSOP-Timestamp: {{ts_now}}
Idempotency-Key: {{snap_dup}}
User-Agent: WSOPLive-ChipCountSync/1.0.0

{
  "snapshot_id": "{{snap_dup}}",
  "break_id": 1024,
  "table_id": 17,
  "recorded_at": "{{ts_now}}",
  "seats": [
    {"seat_number": 1, "player_id": 901, "chip_count": 999999}
  ]
}

###

### E. Idempotency-Key ↔ body.snapshot_id 불일치 → 409 IDEMPOTENCY_MISMATCH
### 기대: {"error": "IDEMPOTENCY_MISMATCH"}
POST {{host}}{{endpoint}}
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
X-WSOP-Signature: {{hmac_valid}}
X-WSOP-Timestamp: {{ts_now}}
Idempotency-Key: 33333333-4444-4555-8666-777777777777
User-Agent: WSOPLive-ChipCountSync/1.0.0

{
  "snapshot_id": "{{snap_mismatch}}",
  "break_id": 1024,
  "table_id": 17,
  "recorded_at": "{{ts_now}}",
  "seats": [
    {"seat_number": 1, "player_id": 901, "chip_count": 125000}
  ]
}

###

### F. 알 수 없는 table_id → 422 TABLE_UNKNOWN
### 기대: {"error": "TABLE_UNKNOWN", "table_id": 99999}
POST {{host}}{{endpoint}}
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
X-WSOP-Signature: {{hmac_valid}}
X-WSOP-Timestamp: {{ts_now}}
Idempotency-Key: {{snap_unknown_table}}
User-Agent: WSOPLive-ChipCountSync/1.0.0

{
  "snapshot_id": "{{snap_unknown_table}}",
  "break_id": 1024,
  "table_id": 99999,
  "recorded_at": "{{ts_now}}",
  "seats": [
    {"seat_number": 1, "player_id": 901, "chip_count": 125000}
  ]
}

###

### G. (회귀, 수동) — chip_count_snapshots audit query
### 본 endpoint 는 §10 of Players_HandHistory_API.md 에서 추가 예정. 현 시점은 직접 DB query.
###
### psql -h localhost -p 5432 -U ebs -c "
###   SELECT snapshot_id, table_id, seat_number, chip_count, recorded_at
###   FROM chip_count_snapshots
###   WHERE table_id = 17 AND break_id = 1024
###   ORDER BY recorded_at DESC, seat_number ASC;
### "
###
### 기대: A 시나리오 1회 실행 후 9 rows. D 재실행해도 변화 없음 (immutable append).
